The paper discusses the study of empirical methodology in navigation research, which involves the use of Artificial Intelligence techniques for mobile operation in three-dimensional environments. This topic is closely related to several sub-fields of Computer Science, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
